Posts.Content: Congratulations!! I was 39 when I was diagnosed and it was a total shock- I was diagnosed with a very very rare type and not much is known about this type. I would love to get more information on your fundraiser. Please e-mail if I can do anything to help. Keep up the great work- together we can find a cure- I am convinced of this. J.
Posts.Title: Fellow Survivors, Help me Reach my Goal!
